[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_0",
    "text": "1.基础单价",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.11750062235499129,
      0.0698782424563261,
      0.23400547672392333,
      0.08611258161284631
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_1",
    "text": "基础单价是计算程单价的基础，包括预算单价，材料预算价格，电、风、预 算价格，施机械使用费，砂料单价，混凝材料单价。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06771222305202888,
      0.09175930827598376,
      0.9290515309932785,
      0.13410975824951474
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_2",
    "text": "（1）预算单价。是指付给从事建筑及安装程施的产的各项费。包 括产的基本资和辅助工资。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07269106298232512,
      0.13763896241397564,
      0.9260642270351008,
      0.17998941238750663
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_3",
    "text": "1）基本资，由技能资和岗位资构成",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11451331839681354,
      0.1842244573848597,
      0.5327358725416977,
      0.20328215987294865
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_4",
    "text": "技能资是根据不同技术岗位对劳动技能的要求和职实际具备的劳动技能平及 作实绩，经考试、考核合格确定的工资。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07368683096838437,
      0.20751720487030176,
      0.9260642270351008,
      0.24986765484383272
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_5",
    "text": "岗位工资是根据职工所在岗位的责任、技能要求、劳动强度和劳动条件的差别所确定 的工资。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06870799103808813,
      0.2533968590082936,
      0.9230769230769231,
      0.2957473089818246
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_6",
    "text": "2）辅助工资，是在基本工资之外，以其他形式支付给职工的工资性收。包括： ①根据国家有关规定属于资性质的各种津贴，主要包括地区津贴、施津贴和加班津贴 等；②产工人年有效施天数以外作业天数的资，包括职工学习、培训期间的工 资，调动作、探亲和休假期间的工资，因候影响的停工资，哺乳时间的资， 病假在6个以内的资及产、婚、丧假期的资。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07169529499626587,
      0.2992765131462855,
      0.9260642270351008,
      0.41150520557614256
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_7",
    "text": "本书仅列出了般地区预算单价计算标准见表11-1。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11451331839681354,
      0.4150344097406035,
      0.6681603186457555,
      0.43409211222869243
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61520788.pdf_391_9",
    "text": "般地区预算单价计算标准 单位：元/工时",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
